TIParticleWeaponTemplate.displayName.LightIonBattery_RapidFire=Light Ion Battery - Rapid Fire
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.description.LightIonBattery_RapidFire=A rapid-fire variant of the Light Ion Battery, designed to unleash a continuous barrage of ionized particles at high velocity. With an increased salvo size and reduced intra-salvo cooldown, this weapon excels at sustained firepower, making it ideal for overwhelming enemy defenses and maintaining pressure during prolonged engagements. The enhanced targeting range allows for greater engagement distances, while the improved efficiency ensures that each shot delivers maximum impact on target.
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.displayName.JitterStreamBattery_I=Jitter Stream Battery I
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.description.JitterStreamBattery_I=The Jitter Stream Battery I is a cutting-edge particle weapon that fires a stream of charged particles with a unique jittering pattern. This design allows the weapon to effectively disrupt enemy targeting systems and increase the likelihood of hitting agile targets. The Jitter Stream Battery I is particularly effective against smaller, faster-moving targets such as missiles and fighter craft, making it an essential component of any ship's defensive arsenal. With its advanced targeting capabilities and high damage output, the Jitter Stream Battery I is a formidable weapon in space combat.
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.displayName.JitterStreamBattery_II=Jitter Stream Battery II
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.description.JitterStreamBattery_II=The Jitter Stream Battery II is an upgraded version of the original Jitter Stream Battery, featuring enhanced particle acceleration technology and improved targeting systems. This iteration delivers a more concentrated and powerful stream of charged particles, increasing its effectiveness against a wider range of targets, including larger ships and fortified structures. The Jitter Stream Battery II's advanced targeting algorithms allow it to adapt its firing pattern in real-time, making it even more effective at tracking and engaging fast-moving targets. With its increased damage output and versatility, the Jitter Stream Battery II is a critical asset for any fleet looking to maintain superiority in space combat.
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.displayName.JitterStreamBattery_III=Jitter Stream Battery III
TIParticleWeaponTemplate.description.JitterStreamBattery_III=The Jitter Stream Battery III represents the pinnacle of particle weapon technology, incorporating the latest advancements in particle acceleration and targeting systems. This version delivers an even more powerful and precise stream of charged particles, capable of inflicting devastating damage on a wide range of targets, from small fighter craft to heavily armored capital ships. The Jitter Stream Battery III's adaptive firing pattern allows it to effectively engage multiple targets simultaneously, making it an invaluable asset in large-scale space battles. With its unparalleled damage output and versatility, the Jitter Stream Battery III is a must-have weapon for any fleet seeking to dominate the battlefield and secure victory in space combat.
